{"id":1733547,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-19T12:19:09.503Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/9mc2aLmPRVY8r1PzsX05N4ozMXn.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Drama"}],"homepage":"https://www.sambogstedt.com/","id":1733547,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["NL"],"original_language":"sv","original_title":"Olyckor i Tillvaron, för en man som lider tyst","overview":"In a vast empty parking garage that seems to stretch without end, Lennart, an aging bank employee, discovers that he can no longer find his car.  What begins as a minor inconvenience slowly transforms into an absurd journey through identical floors, quiet reflections and strange encounters. As he searches the concrete maze, reality starts to bend around him. A mysterious figure appears and disappears, offering riddles instead of answers, while the outside world waits for his return.  Trapped in a cycle of repetition and frustration, Lennart is forced to confront a growing sense of hopelessness. As the search continues, the missing car becomes more than a lost vehicle. It becomes a reflection of a man struggling to regain his control in a world that seems to move forward without him.  Misfortune in Life, for a Man Who Suffers in Silence is an absurdist drama about hopelessness, loss of control, and the quiet fear of being left behind.","popularity":0.0143,"poster_path":"/PuAQCMH3eXQu2LMDQypM0a7xFp.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"NL","name":"Netherlands"}],"release_date":"2026-07-10","revenue":0,"runtime":10,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Swedish","iso_639_1":"sv","name":"svenska"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Misfortune in Life, of a man who suffers in silence","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":3966577,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Rikard Westman","original_name":"Rikard Westman","popularity